items.name: Fencoil
implicitMods: +12% Chance to Block Attack Damage while wielding a Staff
explicitMods: Socketed Gems are Supported by Level 8 Trap
flavourText: You've no reason for fear when you're a root in a fen
- Old Ezomyte saying.

items.name: Reaper's Pursuit
explicitMods: 15% increased Movement Speed when on Full Life
flavourText: Accept your fate, or lie, pretend.
Death collects you in the end.

items.name: Rigwald's Charge
flavourText: "Today, clansmen, my sword is my voice!"
- Rigwald, at the Battle of Glarryn

items.name: The Stormheart
implicitMods: +12% Chance to Block Attack Damage while wielding a Staff
explicitMods: You cannot be Shocked while Frozen
flavourText: When the storm comes,
the safest place to be is the centre.

items.name: Geofri's Baptism
flavourText: "One quick tap is all the persuasion you'll need."
- Archbishop Geofri of Phrecia Cathedral

items.name: Titucius' Span
explicitMods: -10 Physical Damage taken from Projectile Attacks
+25% Chance to Block Projectile Attack Damage
flavourText: A mighty bulwark, curved and strong
A dauntless wall, against the throng
All lance and arrow, knocked aside
For rout of foe, for turn of tide.

items.name: Chober Chaber
explicitMods: +1 to Level of Socketed Melee Gems
+1 to Level of Socketed Minion Gems
flavourText: The faithful may continue to serve, even after death.

items.name: Wideswing
explicitMods: Socketed Gems are Supported by Level 20 Increased Area of Effect
flavourText: Bargg Wurmkin once severed the heads
of seven men in a single cleave.

items.name: Limbsplit
explicitMods: +1 to Level of Socketed Strength Gems
flavourText: Swinging through the air, it sings
of sundered, severed, missing things.

items.name: Geofri's Baptism
flavourText: "One quick tap is all the persuasion you'll need."
- Archbishop Geofri of Phrecia Cathedral

items.name: Pillar of the Caged God
implicitMods: +12% Chance to Block Attack Damage while wielding a Staff
explicitMods: 1% increased Area of Effect per 20 Intelligence
16% increased Physical Weapon Damage per 10 Strength
flavourText: Forged to rule the waves and tide
Destined to serve the monkey's paw
Strong as a tower of iron
Deft as the needle doubt

items.name: Hrimnor's Hymn
explicitMods: 1% of Physical Attack Damage Leeched as Life
flavourText: "The crack of bone, the spray of blood.
Is there sweeter music?"
- Hrimnor of the Ezomytes.
